    <summary>Cross-platform terminal clipboard helper with OSC 52 support</summary>
    <description>
termclip is a pipe-friendly cross-platform clipboard tool that works over SSH and in terminal environments.

## Features
- Works over SSH using OSC 52 sequences
- Cross-platform (Windows, macOS, Linux)
- Falls back to native clipboard tools when available
- Supports tmux and screen multiplexers
- Zero dependencies beyond Python

## Usage
```
echo "hello world" | termclip
termclip --paste
termclip --version
```

## Windows Support
- Uses native PowerShell clipboard when available
- OSC 52 support for Windows Terminal and modern terminals
- Works in Command Prompt, PowerShell, and WSL
    </description>
